name: ChinolaToken
description: ChinolaToken (CHNT) is an ERC-20 token with a maximum supply of 21 trillion tokens, utilizing innovative tokenomics. Each transaction incurs a 1% burn, reducing the supply and potentially increasing token value. Additionally, a 1% transaction fee is allocated to a designated address, providing resources for platform development. Holding limits prevent market manipulation, promoting fairness. CHNT is integrated with Uniswap V2 for liquidity and supports 18 decimal places for precision. Join us to experience the future of decentralized finance and benefit from our balanced token ecosystem.
